show.description: Miss Supreme ka raaz, Emperor ke favorite picks aur ek lord jiska naam hi sab kuch badalne ka signal hai. Ye sirf drama nahi, ek experience hai jisme har scene banata hai history. Par kya aap tayyar ho uss twist ke liye jisse pura plot ulat jayega? Don’t blink… kyunki agla moment hi sabse bada dhamaka ho sakta hai.
